	<name>Dosage</name>
	<summary>Keep track of your treatments</summary>
	<developer_name>Diego Povliuk</developer_name>
	<update_contact>diego.pvlk@gmail.com</update_contact>
	<url type="homepage">https://github.com/diegopvlk/Dosage</url>
	<description>
		<p>Remember to take your medications!</p>
		<p>Features:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Notifications: get reminders on time</li>
			<li>History: keep track of what medications you take or skipped</li>
			<li>Dosages: multiple doses with different times</li>
			<li>Frequency modes: every day, selected days, cycle or when needed</li>
			<li>Color and icon: give a form for your treatment</li>
			<li>Inventory: keep track of your stock and get reminded when it's low</li>
			<li>Duration: set a date to start and end</li>
		</ul>
	</description>
